categories: Category:Unidentified members of the Ohnaka Gang

nodes.text: A burly Weequay pirate served in the Ohnaka Gang during the Clone Wars.

Around 20 BBY, the pirate assisted Hondo Ohnaka and Gwarm in boarding the Crucible to steal Jedi lightsaber crystals on board, though the plan ultimately failed, and resulted in the Ohnaka Gang's base being destroyed.

Later in the year, numerous pirates betrayed Ohnaka and joined Darth Maul and Savage Opress, including this one. After a long skirmish which brought the deaths of countless pirates, the surviving traitors reunited with Hondo, and helped him to chase the brothers off Florrum. The Ohnaka Gang soon ended up with much wealth and weaponry.
